        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: '???', 3: '\"No sooner had rubicund Apollo spread over the face of the wide and spacious earth the golden strands of his beauteous hair, no sooner had diminutive and bright-hued birds with dulcet tongues greeted in sweet, mellifluous harmony the advent of rosy dawn...\"', 4: '1'}"
