        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{3: 'Roland smiles and gives the paper one final press before standing it up on a burnt branch in front of him—it is an origami rabbit.'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 17,
        "ActionId": 17,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Roland', 3: 'Can\\'t you tell...? It\\'s a rabbit. Do you know what a rabbit is?', 4: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 18,
        "ActionId": 18,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{3: 'Cinderelik looks at the paper bunny and frowns.'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 19,
        "ActionId": 19,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Cinderelik', 3: 'I know what it is, but is this a rabbit...?', 4: '2'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 20,
        "ActionId": 20,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Roland', 3: 'I think I did a pretty good job. It\\'s small and white with big eyes and long ears... Isn\\'t it adorable?', 4: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 21,
        "ActionId": 21,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Cinderelik', 3: 'Adorable... How can a creature so weak be adorable? I don\\'t understand why you made it.', 4: '2'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 22,
        "ActionId": 22,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{3: 'Roland stands up from his tree trunk and stretches.'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 23,
        "ActionId": 23,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Roland', 3: 'Maybe... I was bored.', 4: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 24,
        "ActionId": 24,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{3: 'Cinderelik has no idea what the man before her is thinking, but she does not need to know. It was Mister\\'s idea to keep him with them, and Mister is never wrong.'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 25,
        "ActionId": 25,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Cinderelik', 3: 'Mister is looking for you. Come... He told me it\\'s your reward.', 4: '2'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 26,
        "ActionId": 26,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 204,
        "IsBlock": null,
