        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{1: '1', 3: 'Voodoo\\'s voice suddenly becomes metallic and sharp. There seems to be some form of personality breakdown due to the M.I.N.D. defect of a humanoid-hybrid Construct.'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 88,
        "ActionId": 88,
